WEBVTT

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:37.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF A SISTER VENTURING OUT</b></Default>

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:40.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Sakuta sighs]</b></Default>

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:56.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai, is that you?</b></Default>

00:00:58.289 --> 00:00:59.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hi, mister.</b></Default>

00:00:59.420 --> 00:01:00.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do I know you?</b></Default>

00:01:02.750 --> 00:01:05.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I do look a lot
more grown up now, don't I?</b></Default>

00:01:05.959 --> 00:01:07.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My mom told me
that I'm not allowed</b></Default>

00:01:07.829 --> 00:01:10.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to talk to strange old men</b></Default>

00:01:10.959 --> 00:01:13.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So where is
that mom of yours, anyway?</b></Default>

00:01:13.290 --> 00:01:14.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Uh...</b></Default>

00:01:14.459 --> 00:01:16.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, what's the matter?</b></Default>

00:01:16.129 --> 00:01:17.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you lost?</b></Default>

00:01:17.250 --> 00:01:18.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know where I am.</b></Default>

00:01:19.209 --> 00:01:21.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just... don't know
where this is.</b></Default>

00:01:21.579 --> 00:01:23.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Didn't you say
you weren't allowed</b></Default>

00:01:23.170 --> 00:01:25.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to talk to weird old men</b></Default>

00:01:25.540 --> 00:01:26.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Hmm.</b></Default>

00:01:26.750 --> 00:01:27.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fine, then.</b></Default>

00:01:28.959 --> 00:01:30.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] This is Shichirigahama.</b></Default>

00:01:32.459 --> 00:01:35.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's much smaller than the name
actually suggests.</b></Default>

00:01:36.379 --> 00:01:39.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm a student over at
Minegahara High School nearby.</b></Default>

00:01:39.629 --> 00:01:41.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My name is Sakuta Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:01:41.790 --> 00:01:44.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, I'm a little better
than a stranger at least, right?</b></Default>

00:01:50.709 --> 00:01:52.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inaudible]</b></Default>

00:01:55.750 --> 00:01:57.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAN] {\i1}Azusagawa!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:01:58.079 --> 00:01:59.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Hey, Azusagawa.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:02:01.579 --> 00:02:02.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Wake up!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:02:03.420 --> 00:02:04.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTO] Hmm?</b></Default>

00:02:06.079 --> 00:02:07.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good morning, teach.</b></Default>

00:02:07.500 --> 00:02:08.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[students laugh]</b></Default>

00:02:08.580 --> 00:02:09.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Enough of that.</b></Default>

00:02:09.710 --> 00:02:11.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right. Kamisato</b></Default>

00:02:12.080 --> 00:02:13.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Kamisato sighs]</b></Default>

00:02:13.250 --> 00:02:14.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAMISATO] Hmm.</b></Default>

00:02:15.129 --> 00:02:18.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You went to a golf academy
in Australia</b></Default>

00:02:18.789 --> 00:02:20.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you were ten, right?</b></Default>

00:02:20.250 --> 00:02:21.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>FRIDAY, JANUARY 16TH</b></Default>

00:02:21.539 --> 00:02:24.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. At first, I couldn't exp...</b></Default>

00:02:24.629 --> 00:02:27.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[students chattering]
-[school bell chiming]</b></Default>

00:02:33.960 --> 00:02:35.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TEACHER] Azusagawa!</b></Default>

00:02:35.629 --> 00:02:36.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, what's up, teach?</b></Default>

00:02:36.960 --> 00:02:37.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't "what's up" me!</b></Default>

00:02:38.039 --> 00:02:39.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Career path questionnaire.</b></Default>

00:02:39.580 --> 00:02:41.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Submit it by early next week</b></Default>

00:02:42.330 --> 00:02:43.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Oh.</b></Default>

00:02:43.629 --> 00:02:45.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What reaction is that?</b></Default>

00:02:45.250 --> 00:02:47.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you talked to your parents
about it yet?</b></Default>

00:02:48.330 --> 00:02:50.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I'll get it back
to you if I don't forget.</b></Default>

00:02:50.330 --> 00:02:51.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not allowed to forget.</b></Default>

00:02:55.789 --> 00:02:57.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[yawns]</b></Default>

00:02:57.500 --> 00:02:58.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's wrong?</b></Default>

00:02:58.669 --> 00:03:01.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is going home with me
really that boring?</b></Default>

00:03:01.250 --> 00:03:02.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had a bit of a weird dream</b></Default>

00:03:02.919 --> 00:03:04.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I don't think
I ever really woke up.</b></Default>

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:06.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what is wrong
with you</b></Default>

00:03:06.330 --> 00:03:08.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that you woke up
after sixth period is over?</b></Default>

00:03:08.960 --> 00:03:11.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really should be listening
in your classes.</b></Default>

00:03:11.500 --> 00:03:13.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You want to go to university
with me, right?</b></Default>

00:03:13.750 --> 00:03:14.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hang on.</b></Default>

00:03:14.879 --> 00:03:17.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you wanted to go
to the same university as me.</b></Default>

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:19.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, right.</b></Default>

00:03:19.169 --> 00:03:22.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I just love you
more than you love me, huh?</b></Default>

00:03:22.879 --> 00:03:23.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

00:03:23.919 --> 00:03:27.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fine. I'm the one who wants
to go to the same university.</b></Default>

00:03:27.710 --> 00:03:30.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[bell dinging]
-[MAI] Which train is it?</b></Default>

00:03:30.460 --> 00:03:33.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The one for Fujisawa.
You want to run?</b></Default>

00:03:33.250 --> 00:03:36.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you that eager to get home
as soon as possible?</b></Default>

00:03:36.669 --> 00:03:39.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Every time the two of us
stop to wait here</b></Default>

00:03:39.330 --> 00:03:42.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll wish the railroad
crossing never opened.</b></Default>

00:03:42.289 --> 00:03:44.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That all sounds
very inconvenient.</b></Default>

00:03:53.669 --> 00:03:56.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Before I forget...
What kind of dream was it?</b></Default>

00:03:56.379 --> 00:03:57.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Hmm?</b></Default>

00:03:57.419 --> 00:03:58.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You said earlier</b></Default>

00:03:58.539 --> 00:04:00.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you were having
a weird dream in class.</b></Default>

00:04:00.710 --> 00:04:01.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were a kid</b></Default>

00:04:01.710 --> 00:04:03.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and had on an elementary school
backpack.</b></Default>

00:04:04.879 --> 00:04:06.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't look at me like that.</b></Default>

00:04:06.419 --> 00:04:07.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not like
the current version of you</b></Default>

00:04:07.960 --> 00:04:09.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was running around wearing it.</b></Default>

00:04:09.789 --> 00:04:10.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well...</b></Default>

00:04:11.129 --> 00:04:13.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's a pretty strange dream.</b></Default>

00:04:13.080 --> 00:04:15.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't you have a thing
for older women, Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:04:16.879 --> 00:04:18.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI]
But if you're dreaming that...</b></Default>

00:04:19.459 --> 00:04:22.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's not puberty syndrome
or anything, is it?</b></Default>

00:04:22.500 --> 00:04:24.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You might be overthinking this.</b></Default>

00:04:24.579 --> 00:04:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Am I, though?</b></Default>

00:04:25.670 --> 00:04:27.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Puberty syndrome seems
to be drawn to you.</b></Default>

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:29.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, you got me there.</b></Default>

00:04:29.420 --> 00:04:31.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But thanks to
puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:04:31.170 --> 00:04:33.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that you and I
had a chance to meet at all.</b></Default>

00:04:33.329 --> 00:04:34.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Mai sighs]</b></Default>

00:04:35.829 --> 00:04:37.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] We went through a lot.</b></Default>

00:04:37.709 --> 00:04:40.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Yeah</b></Default>

00:04:41.829 --> 00:04:44.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder how
Shoko-chan's been doing.</b></Default>

00:04:54.879 --> 00:04:56.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Welcome home, Kaede!</b></Default>

00:04:59.329 --> 00:05:01.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Oh! Hey there, Mai!</b></Default>

00:05:03.670 --> 00:05:05.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Oh, look!
You're wearing that coat.</b></Default>

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:08.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course. It's my favorite.</b></Default>

00:05:08.379 --> 00:05:09.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You doing well at school?</b></Default>

00:05:09.879 --> 00:05:10.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's all worked up</b></Default>

00:05:10.920 --> 00:05:12.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and heads out
in the mornings now.</b></Default>

00:05:12.629 --> 00:05:14.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right, big brother.</b></Default>

00:05:14.959 --> 00:05:16.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was, uh...</b></Default>

00:05:16.420 --> 00:05:17.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's the matter?</b></Default>

00:05:17.790 --> 00:05:20.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, what are
your plans tomorrow?</b></Default>

00:05:20.250 --> 00:05:23.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, to be honest, I'm hoping
to enjoy my weekend.</b></Default>

00:05:23.379 --> 00:05:25.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm asking if you're free.
Hmm...</b></Default>

00:05:27.500 --> 00:05:29.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to work tomorrow.</b></Default>

00:05:29.209 --> 00:05:31.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>On Sunday</b></Default>

00:05:31.790 --> 00:05:32.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been way too long.</b></Default>

00:05:33.079 --> 00:05:35.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We need to spend some time
fawning over each other.</b></Default>

00:05:35.790 --> 00:05:38.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Hmm.
That's so upsetting.</b></Default>

00:05:38.379 --> 00:05:39.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, good news, Kaede.</b></Default>

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have something
I need to do this weekend.</b></Default>

00:05:42.329 --> 00:05:43.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, is it work again?</b></Default>

00:05:43.709 --> 00:05:45.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, something like that.</b></Default>

00:05:45.540 --> 00:05:46.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like what, though?</b></Default>

00:05:47.709 --> 00:05:50.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see you're walking home
with Sakuta again.</b></Default>

00:05:51.129 --> 00:05:52.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello, Ryoko.</b></Default>

00:05:52.829 --> 00:05:54.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The two of us are dating.</b></Default>

00:05:54.579 --> 00:05:57.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would be weird if
we couldn't walk together.</b></Default>

00:05:57.170 --> 00:05:58.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be upset if I go online</b></Default>

00:05:58.879 --> 00:06:00.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and see a viral photo
of this later.</b></Default>

00:06:00.709 --> 00:06:03.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We already announced publicly
that we're dating.</b></Default>

00:06:03.209 --> 00:06:05.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not like it would be
a big scandal.</b></Default>

00:06:05.290 --> 00:06:07.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know that
you might feel that way</b></Default>

00:06:07.209 --> 00:06:08.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but how many times
have I said--</b></Default>

00:06:08.920 --> 00:06:09.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hear you.</b></Default>

00:06:10.079 --> 00:06:11.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be careful.</b></Default>

00:06:11.209 --> 00:06:12.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay.</b></Default>

00:06:12.290 --> 00:06:14.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hope you're not just saying
what I want to hear.</b></Default>

00:06:15.170 --> 00:06:17.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I have to go shoot
on a drama series</b></Default>

00:06:17.459 --> 00:06:18.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I just booked.</b></Default>

00:06:18.670 --> 00:06:19.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, I want you</b></Default>

00:06:19.920 --> 00:06:22.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to listen to everything
Kaede tells you, okay?</b></Default>

00:06:22.670 --> 00:06:24.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll see you later, Kaede.</b></Default>

00:06:30.829 --> 00:06:32.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Hmm?</b></Default>

00:06:33.920 --> 00:06:35.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Kaede.</b></Default>

00:06:35.459 --> 00:06:36.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

00:06:36.629 --> 00:06:38.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did Mai do something
to make you mad?</b></Default>

00:06:38.709 --> 00:06:40.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, no, of course not!</b></Default>

00:06:40.879 --> 00:06:42.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's so kind.
Beautiful.</b></Default>

00:06:42.959 --> 00:06:44.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's just amazing.</b></Default>

00:06:44.750 --> 00:06:47.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I do is think about how much
I want to be like her.</b></Default>

00:06:47.829 --> 00:06:51.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If that's the case</b></Default>

00:06:51.290 --> 00:06:53.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're the one I'm upset with.</b></Default>

00:06:53.329 --> 00:06:54.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:06:54.420 --> 00:06:56.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are completely
in love with Mai.</b></Default>

00:06:57.079 --> 00:07:00.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course I am. I mean</b></Default>

00:07:01.290 --> 00:07:04.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I know.
I just don't like it.</b></Default>

00:07:05.879 --> 00:07:08.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] So, you got anything
going this weekend?</b></Default>

00:07:08.829 --> 00:07:11.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Thinking about what
Miss Miwako asked.</b></Default>

00:07:11.209 --> 00:07:12.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]
What'd she ask?</b></Default>

00:07:12.540 --> 00:07:14.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Questions
about the future.</b></Default>

00:07:14.329 --> 00:07:16.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Wow. Heavy stuff.</b></Default>

00:07:16.250 --> 00:07:18.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Yeah, I know.</b></Default>

00:07:19.040 --> 00:07:21.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Whose future?
-About mine, you dummy!</b></Default>

00:07:21.709 --> 00:07:23.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, of course it is.</b></Default>

00:07:24.290 --> 00:07:26.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Miss Miwako was saying earlier
that I should try</b></Default>

00:07:26.829 --> 00:07:29.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>bringing this subject up
with dad, too.</b></Default>

00:07:29.129 --> 00:07:32.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You figured out what you want
to do with your life, yet?</b></Default>

00:07:32.329 --> 00:07:34.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You say that like I can just...</b></Default>

00:07:35.420 --> 00:07:37.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] This all feels
really sudden.</b></Default>

00:07:37.790 --> 00:07:38.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know.</b></Default>

00:07:39.379 --> 00:07:40.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[elevator bell rings]</b></Default>

00:07:41.879 --> 00:07:44.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}SUNDAY, JANUARY 18TH</b></Default>

00:07:44.920 --> 00:07:46.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry.</b></Default>

00:07:46.209 --> 00:07:48.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know it's rude to drop in
on a Sunday.</b></Default>

00:07:48.750 --> 00:07:49.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's no trouble.</b></Default>

00:07:49.959 --> 00:07:51.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you for coming.</b></Default>

00:07:51.790 --> 00:07:52.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your tea.</b></Default>

00:07:52.879 --> 00:07:54.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, thank you.</b></Default>

00:07:54.629 --> 00:07:56.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, to the point...</b></Default>

00:07:56.670 --> 00:07:59.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Will Kaede be able to attend
a standard high school?</b></Default>

00:07:59.790 --> 00:08:01.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looking at her test results</b></Default>

00:08:01.379 --> 00:08:03.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the schools that
will accept her are limited.</b></Default>

00:08:03.959 --> 00:08:05.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are a few places
that will accept her</b></Default>

00:08:06.040 --> 00:08:09.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with these grades.
She will have a few options.</b></Default>

00:08:09.170 --> 00:08:10.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I understand.</b></Default>

00:08:10.959 --> 00:08:13.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The grades on her application
will matter more</b></Default>

00:08:13.170 --> 00:08:14.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for a prefectural school.</b></Default>

00:08:14.709 --> 00:08:15.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Exactly.</b></Default>

00:08:16.040 --> 00:08:17.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As she is</b></Default>

00:08:17.459 --> 00:08:19.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>her grades would put
her request to enroll</b></Default>

00:08:19.829 --> 00:08:21.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at a disadvantage.</b></Default>

00:08:21.290 --> 00:08:22.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are private schools</b></Default>

00:08:22.709 --> 00:08:25.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that base entrance solely
on a student's exam results.</b></Default>

00:08:25.920 --> 00:08:27.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But as a school counselor</b></Default>

00:08:27.750 --> 00:08:30.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am hesitant to recommend them
wholeheartedly.</b></Default>

00:08:30.959 --> 00:08:33.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For cases of non-attendance
in middle school students</b></Default>

00:08:34.039 --> 00:08:35.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there's quite a high
percentage</b></Default>

00:08:35.580 --> 00:08:38.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of those issues continuing
in high school.</b></Default>

00:08:38.539 --> 00:08:41.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are even students
that ultimately drop out.</b></Default>

00:08:42.129 --> 00:08:43.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For high school</b></Default>

00:08:43.379 --> 00:08:46.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there are a few options
other than full time.</b></Default>

00:08:46.169 --> 00:08:48.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Each place has
its own specializations</b></Default>

00:08:48.879 --> 00:08:51.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but all of them offer
remote options now.</b></Default>

00:08:51.330 --> 00:08:53.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}One advantage
of remote schooling</b></Default>

00:08:53.250 --> 00:08:54.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}is watching video lectures</b></Default>

00:08:54.879 --> 00:08:57.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}and studying in your own home
on your own time.</b></Default>

00:08:57.710 --> 00:08:59.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You wouldn't need
to worry about</b></Default>

00:08:59.330 --> 00:09:01.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>fitting in with your classmates.</b></Default>

00:09:01.250 --> 00:09:03.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And in terms of meeting
graduation requirements</b></Default>

00:09:03.919 --> 00:09:06.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there's no difference between
full time and online.</b></Default>

00:09:06.500 --> 00:09:08.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When it comes to online schools</b></Default>

00:09:08.419 --> 00:09:10.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've heard the dropout rates
are high.</b></Default>

00:09:10.580 --> 00:09:12.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At least when compared
to graduation rates</b></Default>

00:09:12.710 --> 00:09:14.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of full time schools.</b></Default>

00:09:14.500 --> 00:09:16.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm afraid that's correct.</b></Default>

00:09:16.330 --> 00:09:18.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I won't pretend
the online option</b></Default>

00:09:18.330 --> 00:09:20.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>works perfectly
for every student.</b></Default>

00:09:20.539 --> 00:09:24.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It requires a healthy pace
for studying independently.</b></Default>

00:09:24.669 --> 00:09:26.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's also important</b></Default>

00:09:26.250 --> 00:09:28.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to have support at home
to help guide them.</b></Default>

00:09:30.330 --> 00:09:32.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Kaede, what do you
want to do?</b></Default>

00:09:32.379 --> 00:09:33.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Kaede exclaims]</b></Default>

00:09:35.129 --> 00:09:36.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] I want...</b></Default>

00:09:41.419 --> 00:09:42.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess...</b></Default>

00:09:43.289 --> 00:09:45.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want what everyone wants.</b></Default>

00:09:45.879 --> 00:09:46.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does that mean you would</b></Default>

00:09:47.039 --> 00:09:49.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like to go
to a full-time campus, Kaede?</b></Default>

00:09:49.960 --> 00:09:51.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Mm-hmm.</b></Default>

00:09:51.169 --> 00:09:54.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is there a specific school
you'd like to go to?</b></Default>

00:09:54.129 --> 00:09:55.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, there is.</b></Default>

00:09:56.129 --> 00:09:58.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It doesn't cost anything
to say it.</b></Default>

00:09:59.960 --> 00:10:02.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to apply
where big brother is.</b></Default>

00:10:03.210 --> 00:10:06.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really want us to go
to school together.</b></Default>

00:10:06.629 --> 00:10:07.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

00:10:07.919 --> 00:10:10.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You could have said
that earlier, you know.</b></Default>

00:10:12.460 --> 00:10:14.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not in favor of Kaede</b></Default>

00:10:14.629 --> 00:10:17.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>applying to
Minegahara High School.</b></Default>

00:10:17.629 --> 00:10:19.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At her current academic level</b></Default>

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:23.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she has a very low likelihood
of being accepted.</b></Default>

00:10:23.129 --> 00:10:25.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd like to prepare her
for a career path</b></Default>

00:10:25.500 --> 00:10:26.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's more realistic.</b></Default>

00:10:27.000 --> 00:10:27.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

00:10:32.789 --> 00:10:34.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door closes]</b></Default>

00:10:40.129 --> 00:10:42.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder if she hates me now.</b></Default>

00:10:42.379 --> 00:10:43.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't worry about it.</b></Default>

00:10:43.879 --> 00:10:46.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She'll forget as soon as
she eats some pudding.</b></Default>

00:10:46.919 --> 00:10:49.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[clattering]
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:10:50.539 --> 00:10:52.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're going back already?</b></Default>

00:10:52.210 --> 00:10:53.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:10:53.379 --> 00:10:54.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What about Kaede?</b></Default>

00:10:54.789 --> 00:10:55.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's in her room.</b></Default>

00:10:56.080 --> 00:10:58.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She responded when
I said I was leaving.</b></Default>

00:10:58.289 --> 00:11:00.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-She'll be fine.
-I see.</b></Default>

00:11:01.250 --> 00:11:02.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakata.</b></Default>

00:11:02.419 --> 00:11:03.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:11:03.500 --> 00:11:05.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you know what your plans are?</b></Default>

00:11:05.379 --> 00:11:07.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to university.</b></Default>

00:11:07.250 --> 00:11:09.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to try to earn
my own tuition</b></Default>

00:11:09.210 --> 00:11:10.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as much as I can.</b></Default>

00:11:11.710 --> 00:11:14.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if I run short</b></Default>

00:11:14.330 --> 00:11:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please.</b></Default>

00:11:16.330 --> 00:11:18.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right. [chuckles]</b></Default>

00:11:18.580 --> 00:11:20.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's with the laugh?</b></Default>

00:11:20.080 --> 00:11:21.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm counting on you.</b></Default>

00:11:21.629 --> 00:11:22.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With Kaede.</b></Default>

00:11:33.210 --> 00:11:34.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:11:38.419 --> 00:11:39.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Say ahh!</b></Default>

00:11:40.210 --> 00:11:41.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}Ahh!</b></Default>

00:11:41.539 --> 00:11:43.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}MONDAY, JANUARY 19TH</b></Default>

00:11:44.419 --> 00:11:45.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mmm.</b></Default>

00:11:47.250 --> 00:11:49.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, that was
a really good lunch.</b></Default>

00:11:49.289 --> 00:11:50.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you for making it.</b></Default>

00:11:51.250 --> 00:11:52.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was nothing at all.</b></Default>

00:11:52.830 --> 00:11:55.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can I ask what brought this on
all of a sudden?</b></Default>

00:11:55.250 --> 00:11:56.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No reason.</b></Default>

00:11:56.419 --> 00:11:59.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just had an urge
to make you lunch, that's all.</b></Default>

00:12:02.750 --> 00:12:04.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh! What's this?</b></Default>

00:12:04.169 --> 00:12:06.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An answer sheet
for an admissions test.</b></Default>

00:12:06.669 --> 00:12:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like, from a past exam?</b></Default>

00:12:08.330 --> 00:12:10.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nope. For this year.</b></Default>

00:12:10.580 --> 00:12:13.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. Uh, why are you practicing
for this year?</b></Default>

00:12:13.830 --> 00:12:15.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've been working
on this mock exam</b></Default>

00:12:15.460 --> 00:12:16.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the last few days</b></Default>

00:12:16.419 --> 00:12:18.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'm checking my score.
It's useful.</b></Default>

00:12:18.750 --> 00:12:20.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just put in the answers
on my phone</b></Default>

00:12:20.750 --> 00:12:22.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I can see my result.</b></Default>

00:12:22.750 --> 00:12:25.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hang on. You're gonna take
the exam this year?</b></Default>

00:12:25.419 --> 00:12:26.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you were gonna
wait a year</b></Default>

00:12:26.669 --> 00:12:27.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and take some time off</b></Default>

00:12:27.669 --> 00:12:29.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so we could enroll
as freshmen together.</b></Default>

00:12:29.460 --> 00:12:31.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to get it
out of the way this year.</b></Default>

00:12:31.330 --> 00:12:33.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I'll take time off
before we start.</b></Default>

00:12:33.250 --> 00:12:35.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought it might
motivate you to study</b></Default>

00:12:35.330 --> 00:12:37.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like your life
depended on it, too.</b></Default>

00:12:37.289 --> 00:12:38.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs, exclaims]</b></Default>

00:12:39.039 --> 00:12:40.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you thinking
it'd be better</b></Default>

00:12:40.500 --> 00:12:41.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if I didn't get accepted?</b></Default>

00:12:41.919 --> 00:12:42.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Of course not.</b></Default>

00:12:42.960 --> 00:12:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was thinking I might want
something to get me pumped</b></Default>

00:12:45.330 --> 00:12:46.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for all that work, that's all.</b></Default>

00:12:46.960 --> 00:12:48.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

00:12:48.129 --> 00:12:50.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How about we go on a date
after school, then?</b></Default>

00:12:50.419 --> 00:12:51.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't have work today.</b></Default>

00:12:51.919 --> 00:12:55.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I heard that Innoshima has
a tulip super bloom right now.</b></Default>

00:12:55.379 --> 00:12:57.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]
Oh, I have something today.</b></Default>

00:12:57.960 --> 00:12:59.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Working?</b></Default>

00:12:59.330 --> 00:13:01.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, something like that.</b></Default>

00:13:01.539 --> 00:13:03.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you do that
to get back at me?</b></Default>

00:13:03.750 --> 00:13:04.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Ow, ow, ow!</b></Default>

00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:11.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm? Oh, hey.</b></Default>

00:13:11.250 --> 00:13:12.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you scheduled to work today?</b></Default>

00:13:12.960 --> 00:13:14.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm just meeting up
with someone.</b></Default>

00:13:14.580 --> 00:13:15.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you meeting your girlfriend?</b></Default>

00:13:15.960 --> 00:13:16.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not right now.</b></Default>

00:13:17.250 --> 00:13:19.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Try not to cheat on her
if you can help it.</b></Default>

00:13:19.539 --> 00:13:21.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hey, Kunimi.
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:13:21.960 --> 00:13:24.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you have any big plans
after your graduation?</b></Default>

00:13:24.750 --> 00:13:27.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Probably take the test
to be a firefighter.</b></Default>

00:13:28.039 --> 00:13:29.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Glad to know
I'll be in good hands</b></Default>

00:13:29.710 --> 00:13:31.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when my house is on fire.</b></Default>

00:13:31.129 --> 00:13:33.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You shouldn't play
with matches anyway.</b></Default>

00:13:33.379 --> 00:13:35.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you tell Futaba that, too?</b></Default>

00:13:35.460 --> 00:13:37.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, and she said
she'll be careful.</b></Default>

00:13:37.710 --> 00:13:39.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, hi!</b></Default>

00:13:39.419 --> 00:13:40.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did I make you wait?</b></Default>

00:13:41.000 --> 00:13:43.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I just got here
a few minutes ago.</b></Default>

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:53.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta definitely has a thing
for older women.</b></Default>

00:13:54.960 --> 00:13:56.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm home.</b></Default>

00:13:59.210 --> 00:14:01.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh?
-[chopping]</b></Default>

00:14:01.960 --> 00:14:03.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is someone here?</b></Default>

00:14:03.419 --> 00:14:05.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh! Welcome home, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:14:05.580 --> 00:14:07.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought I'd borrow
the kitchen.</b></Default>

00:14:07.330 --> 00:14:08.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing here?</b></Default>

00:14:09.210 --> 00:14:11.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I bumped into Kaede downstairs
on my way back.</b></Default>

00:14:12.080 --> 00:14:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You forgot to tell your sister
you had something going on, huh?</b></Default>

00:14:15.330 --> 00:14:18.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you came over and decided
to make dinner for Kaede</b></Default>

00:14:18.330 --> 00:14:19.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because you thought
there might be a chance</b></Default>

00:14:20.000 --> 00:14:21.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would be back home too late?</b></Default>

00:14:21.379 --> 00:14:22.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOYOHAMA] You're back.</b></Default>

00:14:22.750 --> 00:14:25.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What exactly is Toyohama
doing here?</b></Default>

00:14:25.289 --> 00:14:27.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My big sis said she was
eating dinner at your place</b></Default>

00:14:27.669 --> 00:14:29.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I decided to tag along.</b></Default>

00:14:29.250 --> 00:14:30.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You shouldn't tag along.</b></Default>

00:14:30.539 --> 00:14:32.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's time to leave the nest.</b></Default>

00:14:32.129 --> 00:14:33.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:14:33.080 --> 00:14:35.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, did Sweet Bullet's
live video come out?</b></Default>

00:14:36.039 --> 00:14:37.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}[TOYOHAMA]
It's from our concert.</b></Default>

00:14:37.460 --> 00:14:39.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}They gave us some samples</b></Default>

00:14:39.879 --> 00:14:41.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then we should have
a screening party.</b></Default>

00:14:41.919 --> 00:14:43.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do not do that.</b></Default>

00:14:43.250 --> 00:14:45.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm trying to tutor Kaede
in English right now.</b></Default>

00:14:45.830 --> 00:14:48.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing less from
our highly-educated idol.</b></Default>

00:14:48.330 --> 00:14:49.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

00:14:52.289 --> 00:14:54.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's something you want
to tell him, isn't there?</b></Default>

00:14:55.210 --> 00:14:56.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:14:58.000 --> 00:14:59.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chair scrapes on floor]</b></Default>

00:15:01.500 --> 00:15:02.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I... I was...</b></Default>

00:15:03.379 --> 00:15:04.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I... Umm...</b></Default>

00:15:05.330 --> 00:15:06.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was hoping...</b></Default>

00:15:08.379 --> 00:15:09.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted...</b></Default>

00:15:09.960 --> 00:15:13.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really want to go to
the same high school as you.</b></Default>

00:15:15.960 --> 00:15:17.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

00:15:23.960 --> 00:15:25.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here. Fill this out.</b></Default>

00:15:25.789 --> 00:15:26.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:15:27.879 --> 00:15:29.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>KANAGAWA PREFECTURAL
MINEGAHARA HIGH SCHOOL</b></Default>

00:15:29.250 --> 00:15:31.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>ENROLLMENT APPLICATION
(FULL-TIME)</b></Default>

00:15:31.500 --> 00:15:33.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exclaims softly]</b></Default>

00:15:34.210 --> 00:15:36.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I got one from Tomobe
earlier today</b></Default>

00:15:37.960 --> 00:15:40.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so make sure you study hard.</b></Default>

00:15:41.830 --> 00:15:43.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll do my best.</b></Default>

00:15:43.580 --> 00:15:46.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I have a favor
I need to ask you.</b></Default>

00:15:46.210 --> 00:15:47.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:15:47.919 --> 00:15:50.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think...
you could tutor me?</b></Default>

00:15:51.500 --> 00:15:52.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:15:53.039 --> 00:15:54.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

00:15:55.379 --> 00:15:57.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

00:15:58.919 --> 00:16:01.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't blame me if you don't
get accepted, okay?</b></Default>

00:16:04.960 --> 00:16:05.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}SCIENCE CLUB COFFEE</b></Default>

00:16:06.039 --> 00:16:07.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}TUESDAY, JANUARY 20TH</b></Default>

00:16:07.789 --> 00:16:10.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}-I have a question for you.
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:16:10.580 --> 00:16:12.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you going to apply
to the same university</b></Default>

00:16:12.879 --> 00:16:15.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as Sakurajima, or am I wrong
about that?</b></Default>

00:16:15.289 --> 00:16:17.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I am. I thought
I told you before.</b></Default>

00:16:17.580 --> 00:16:20.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because of that, studying for
entrance exams is awful.</b></Default>

00:16:20.330 --> 00:16:22.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You haven't seemed
to notice yet.</b></Default>

00:16:22.129 --> 00:16:24.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I'm going to tell you
something as a friend.</b></Default>

00:16:24.419 --> 00:16:25.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what's that?</b></Default>

00:16:25.710 --> 00:16:28.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The answer key you're using
is for the high school exams.</b></Default>

00:16:28.960 --> 00:16:30.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something you want
to talk about?</b></Default>

00:16:30.919 --> 00:16:34.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. I'm reviewing the material
I need to help Kaede with.</b></Default>

00:16:34.500 --> 00:16:36.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm relieved to hear
it's intentional.</b></Default>

00:16:37.169 --> 00:16:39.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She wants to apply
for a prefectural school?</b></Default>

00:16:39.789 --> 00:16:40.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:16:40.830 --> 00:16:42.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said she wanted
to apply to go here.</b></Default>

00:16:43.129 --> 00:16:44.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

00:16:45.289 --> 00:16:47.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That must be quite hard
to juggle at home.</b></Default>

00:16:48.000 --> 00:16:50.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly, you already saved me
quite a bit.</b></Default>

00:16:50.629 --> 00:16:51.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:16:51.629 --> 00:16:53.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You tutored her over the summer.</b></Default>

00:16:53.879 --> 00:16:57.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, but that was before Kaede
had regained all her memories.</b></Default>

00:16:57.210 --> 00:17:00.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know. I don't think
she really remembers</b></Default>

00:17:00.080 --> 00:17:01.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when she studied back then</b></Default>

00:17:01.629 --> 00:17:04.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I do think she remembers
what she studied about.</b></Default>

00:17:04.420 --> 00:17:07.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you came here because
you wanted to tell me this?</b></Default>

00:17:07.250 --> 00:17:08.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was free before work</b></Default>

00:17:08.579 --> 00:17:10.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I just came here
to kill some time.</b></Default>

00:17:10.750 --> 00:17:12.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, regardless
of today's reason</b></Default>

00:17:12.789 --> 00:17:14.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad
you weren't consulting me</b></Default>

00:17:14.380 --> 00:17:15.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about puberty syndrome again.</b></Default>

00:17:16.000 --> 00:17:19.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Oh. About that...
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:17:19.210 --> 00:17:21.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had a dream about Mai
where she looked very young.</b></Default>

00:17:21.960 --> 00:17:23.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you think that means?</b></Default>

00:17:23.380 --> 00:17:25.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a premonition that
you're going to prison.</b></Default>

00:17:25.960 --> 00:17:27.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No worries there.</b></Default>

00:17:27.250 --> 00:17:29.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think Mai, as she is</b></Default>

00:17:29.670 --> 00:17:32.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But seriously though</b></Default>

00:17:32.250 --> 00:17:33.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does it matter what it means?</b></Default>

00:17:34.000 --> 00:17:35.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why wouldn't it matter?</b></Default>

00:17:35.460 --> 00:17:38.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if the dream you had
was puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:17:38.130 --> 00:17:40.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in some form, it's all going
to work out fine in the end.</b></Default>

00:17:40.960 --> 00:17:42.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really think so?</b></Default>

00:17:42.130 --> 00:17:43.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It doesn't matter what happens</b></Default>

00:17:44.039 --> 00:17:46.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you'll always make do somehow.</b></Default>

00:17:46.329 --> 00:17:49.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just what kind of guy
do you think I am, Futaba?</b></Default>

00:17:49.460 --> 00:17:52.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think you're surprisingly
reliable.</b></Default>

00:17:52.380 --> 00:17:53.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

00:17:53.750 --> 00:17:56.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have done enough for me
to say that confidently.</b></Default>

00:17:56.380 --> 00:17:57.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, the things you're saying</b></Default>

00:17:57.630 --> 00:17:59.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are kind of making me
feel queasy.</b></Default>

00:17:59.880 --> 00:18:03.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's only so much stuff that
I can try to pull off on my own.</b></Default>

00:18:04.630 --> 00:18:08.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}FRIDAY, JANUARY 23RD</b></Default>

00:18:08.170 --> 00:18:09.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>WONDERFUL ENGLISH VOCABULARY</b></Default>

00:18:09.500 --> 00:18:10.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens, closes]</b></Default>

00:18:10.579 --> 00:18:12.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What you got going on there</b></Default>

00:18:12.829 --> 00:18:14.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What does it look like
I'm doing?</b></Default>

00:18:14.630 --> 00:18:16.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like
you're studying to me.</b></Default>

00:18:16.500 --> 00:18:17.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Correct.</b></Default>

00:18:17.829 --> 00:18:20.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, uh, you're going
to go to college?</b></Default>

00:18:20.210 --> 00:18:21.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I get accepted.</b></Default>

00:18:21.630 --> 00:18:23.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What about work?
Are you quitting?</b></Default>

00:18:23.920 --> 00:18:25.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, I guess
I don't really care.</b></Default>

00:18:26.039 --> 00:18:27.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll continue working.</b></Default>

00:18:27.670 --> 00:18:30.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll need the money
one way or another.</b></Default>

00:18:30.380 --> 00:18:31.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, okay.</b></Default>

00:18:31.960 --> 00:18:33.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

00:18:35.289 --> 00:18:37.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have something important
I wanted to say.</b></Default>

00:18:37.579 --> 00:18:40.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What? It's not
something weird, is it?</b></Default>

00:18:40.329 --> 00:18:42.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think your skirt might be
a bit too tight, Koga.</b></Default>

00:18:42.880 --> 00:18:43.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exclaims]</b></Default>

00:18:43.920 --> 00:18:45.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You sure you're wearing
the right size?</b></Default>

00:18:45.460 --> 00:18:47.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course I am.
This is mine.</b></Default>

00:18:47.750 --> 00:18:50.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe you should ask the manager
if you can go a size up.</b></Default>

00:18:50.710 --> 00:18:52.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am not doing that.</b></Default>

00:18:55.460 --> 00:18:56.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:18:57.000 --> 00:18:58.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that a customer?</b></Default>

00:18:59.500 --> 00:19:00.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I'll get her.</b></Default>

00:19:00.960 --> 00:19:02.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's my little sister.</b></Default>

00:19:02.630 --> 00:19:04.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, she is?</b></Default>

00:19:04.130 --> 00:19:05.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's right.</b></Default>

00:19:05.210 --> 00:19:07.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I remember
you mentioning her before.</b></Default>

00:19:08.420 --> 00:19:09.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you come here alone?</b></Default>

00:19:09.750 --> 00:19:11.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, hey, big bro.</b></Default>

00:19:11.250 --> 00:19:12.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I, uh...</b></Default>

00:19:12.880 --> 00:19:15.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, you brought Mai with you.</b></Default>

00:19:15.250 --> 00:19:17.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI]
That "oh" sounded disappointed.</b></Default>

00:19:17.380 --> 00:19:19.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I'm glad that
you're worrying about me</b></Default>

00:19:19.630 --> 00:19:21.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>while I'm still stuck at work.</b></Default>

00:19:21.210 --> 00:19:22.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I went by your place
with a souvenir</b></Default>

00:19:22.880 --> 00:19:24.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I brought from my shoot
in Nagasaki.</b></Default>

00:19:24.670 --> 00:19:27.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede says she hasn't had
her dinner yet.</b></Default>

00:19:27.500 --> 00:19:30.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to submit my application
next week.</b></Default>

00:19:30.329 --> 00:19:31.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. You do.</b></Default>

00:19:31.579 --> 00:19:34.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I need to take it
to the school campus by myself.</b></Default>

00:19:34.539 --> 00:19:36.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I thought I could practice
making the trip.</b></Default>

00:19:37.039 --> 00:19:38.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even though Mai has come
with you</b></Default>

00:19:39.000 --> 00:19:40.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm surprised you made it here.</b></Default>

00:19:40.630 --> 00:19:43.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was better than heading out
in my school uniform.</b></Default>

00:19:43.630 --> 00:19:46.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was a little scary
outside the station</b></Default>

00:19:46.170 --> 00:19:47.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there were so many people.</b></Default>

00:19:48.130 --> 00:19:50.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, wow. You worked hard.</b></Default>

00:19:50.920 --> 00:19:52.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? [chuckles]</b></Default>

00:19:56.079 --> 00:19:57.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]
Thank you so much for waiting.</b></Default>

00:19:57.789 --> 00:20:00.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is your pasta combo
and omelet rice.</b></Default>

00:20:00.920 --> 00:20:02.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This looks good.</b></Default>

00:20:02.630 --> 00:20:04.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then let's hurry and eat.</b></Default>

00:20:04.210 --> 00:20:05.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yes.</b></Default>

00:20:05.210 --> 00:20:06.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Time to dig in.</b></Default>

00:20:06.460 --> 00:20:08.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't mind if I do.</b></Default>

00:20:19.880 --> 00:20:21.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] {\i1}My cheeks are so full!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:21.630 --> 00:20:23.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Big brother</b></Default>

00:20:23.630 --> 00:20:25.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}are they gonna fall off?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:25.750 --> 00:20:27.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something wrong?</b></Default>

00:20:27.289 --> 00:20:28.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:20:28.380 --> 00:20:30.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's hard to eat when
you're staring like that.</b></Default>

00:20:30.920 --> 00:20:33.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm fine. Nothing going on.</b></Default>

00:20:33.210 --> 00:20:35.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not gonna talk me
out of worrying about you</b></Default>

00:20:35.420 --> 00:20:36.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if I want to.</b></Default>

00:20:36.630 --> 00:20:38.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You look like you were
a million miles away.</b></Default>

00:20:39.079 --> 00:20:40.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really?</b></Default>

00:20:40.210 --> 00:20:42.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I'm like this every day.</b></Default>

00:20:42.289 --> 00:20:43.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Isn't that right, Mai?</b></Default>

00:20:43.630 --> 00:20:44.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. That's right.</b></Default>

00:20:44.880 --> 00:20:46.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta is like this every day.</b></Default>

00:20:52.079 --> 00:20:54.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I just feel like...</b></Default>

00:20:54.210 --> 00:20:55.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's up?</b></Default>

00:20:58.579 --> 00:21:00.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] It's nothing.
Never mind.</b></Default>

00:21:01.789 --> 00:21:03.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, that's right.</b></Default>

00:21:03.130 --> 00:21:04.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to ask
if you were working</b></Default>

00:21:04.710 --> 00:21:05.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the next two days.</b></Default>

00:21:05.960 --> 00:21:09.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm. I'm pretty sure
I'm working both days.</b></Default>

00:21:09.170 --> 00:21:10.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay.</b></Default>

00:21:10.289 --> 00:21:12.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I'll have to
start tutoring you at night.</b></Default>

00:21:12.579 --> 00:21:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then you can study with me
in the afternoon.</b></Default>

00:21:15.329 --> 00:21:17.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. Do you have the time off?</b></Default>

00:21:17.170 --> 00:21:19.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, they changed
the filming schedule</b></Default>

00:21:19.539 --> 00:21:21.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I have both days off
this weekend.</b></Default>

00:21:22.039 --> 00:21:24.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was hoping we could
go out on a date</b></Default>

00:21:24.210 --> 00:21:25.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>sometime soon.</b></Default>

00:21:25.289 --> 00:21:27.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess we can't
if you're working.</b></Default>

00:21:28.670 --> 00:21:29.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm...</b></Default>

00:21:31.170 --> 00:21:34.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}SUNDAY, JANUARY 25TH</b></Default>

00:21:43.329 --> 00:21:44.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:21:46.079 --> 00:21:47.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you have any trouble?</b></Default>

00:21:47.750 --> 00:21:49.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't switch trains
to get here.</b></Default>

00:21:49.789 --> 00:21:51.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I meant in the station.</b></Default>

00:21:51.630 --> 00:21:53.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your head is so thick, you know.</b></Default>

00:21:53.630 --> 00:21:55.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sometimes it's a pain
to deal with.</b></Default>

00:21:55.920 --> 00:21:58.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I appreciate
you coming in with me</b></Default>

00:21:58.170 --> 00:21:59.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on your day off.</b></Default>

00:21:59.289 --> 00:22:00.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's fine.</b></Default>

00:22:00.420 --> 00:22:01.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was hoping
I could ask you</b></Default>

00:22:02.039 --> 00:22:04.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to participate in this school
orientation anyway.</b></Default>

00:22:05.250 --> 00:22:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I was relieved to hear you
bring this subject up.</b></Default>

00:22:08.329 --> 00:22:09.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I'm sure it'd
be better</b></Default>

00:22:09.829 --> 00:22:11.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if Kaede were able
to attend herself.</b></Default>

00:22:11.960 --> 00:22:14.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIWAKO] Of course, that's
always the best option.</b></Default>

00:22:14.539 --> 00:22:17.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But she still has
her entrance exams, right?</b></Default>

00:22:17.539 --> 00:22:19.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you said that
you were against her applying</b></Default>

00:22:19.920 --> 00:22:21.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to a prefectural school.</b></Default>

00:22:21.670 --> 00:22:23.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As a school counselor, I am.</b></Default>

00:22:23.960 --> 00:22:25.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's something
I've always been able</b></Default>

00:22:25.829 --> 00:22:27.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to admire you for.</b></Default>

00:22:27.079 --> 00:22:28.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, thank you.</b></Default>

00:22:28.920 --> 00:22:30.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIWAKO] So how do you feel
about it, then?</b></Default>

00:22:31.000 --> 00:22:32.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] About what?</b></Default>

00:22:32.130 --> 00:22:35.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIWAKO] Kaede's entrance exam.
Do you think she'll be accepted?</b></Default>

00:22:35.880 --> 00:22:38.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, I'm hoping that
she'll be accepted.</b></Default>

00:22:38.420 --> 00:22:39.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think you realize it</b></Default>

00:22:40.039 --> 00:22:42.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but your answers
can be snarky sometimes.</b></Default>

00:22:42.789 --> 00:22:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right, well</b></Default>

00:22:45.380 --> 00:22:47.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that it will be hard for her
to get accepted</b></Default>

00:22:48.079 --> 00:22:49.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but she's not going to give up</b></Default>

00:22:49.289 --> 00:22:50.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until she actually
