RECEPTION UP AHEAD</b></Default>

00:29:51.920 --> 00:29:53.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Excuse me.</b></Default>

00:29:53.130 --> 00:29:54.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes?</b></Default>

00:29:54.289 --> 00:29:55.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is there an application</b></Default>

00:29:55.539 --> 00:29:57.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from someone named
Kaede Azusagawa?</b></Default>

00:29:57.670 --> 00:29:58.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

00:29:58.710 --> 00:30:00.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, she's my little sister.</b></Default>

00:30:00.710 --> 00:30:02.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's been home-schooled
for a long time.</b></Default>

00:30:02.630 --> 00:30:04.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was worried
about her getting it in.</b></Default>

00:30:05.289 --> 00:30:06.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on just a minute.</b></Default>

00:30:11.289 --> 00:30:13.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you sure you can submit it
on your own?</b></Default>

00:30:13.880 --> 00:30:15.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be all right.</b></Default>

00:30:16.039 --> 00:30:17.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No application yet.</b></Default>

00:30:17.829 --> 00:30:19.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you very much.</b></Default>

00:30:22.079 --> 00:30:23.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hope she's okay.</b></Default>

00:30:47.539 --> 00:30:48.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:31:03.000 --> 00:31:04.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}[door opens]</b></Default>

00:31:04.289 --> 00:31:06.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}ENTRANCE APPLICATION
RECEPTION UP AHEAD</b></Default>

00:31:07.420 --> 00:31:08.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:31:08.710 --> 00:31:11.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are you surprised?
You came to apply, right?</b></Default>

00:31:12.210 --> 00:31:13.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:31:15.210 --> 00:31:16.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello there.</b></Default>

00:31:16.539 --> 00:31:17.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello.</b></Default>

00:31:17.789 --> 00:31:19.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're turning in
an application?</b></Default>

00:31:19.920 --> 00:31:20.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

00:31:25.880 --> 00:31:27.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Kaede breathing shakily]</b></Default>

00:31:32.380 --> 00:31:33.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here it is.</b></Default>

00:31:34.000 --> 00:31:34.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WOMAN] Yes.</b></Default>

00:31:34.960 --> 00:31:36.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's see.</b></Default>

00:31:36.130 --> 00:31:38.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're Miss Kaede Azusagawa?</b></Default>

00:31:38.210 --> 00:31:39.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Yes.</b></Default>

00:31:39.289 --> 00:31:41.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WOMAN] Okay, we have received
your application.</b></Default>

00:31:41.829 --> 00:31:43.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good luck on your exam.</b></Default>

00:31:43.500 --> 00:31:44.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

00:31:45.880 --> 00:31:46.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother!</b></Default>

00:31:46.960 --> 00:31:48.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are you here?</b></Default>

00:31:48.670 --> 00:31:50.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I needed to use the toilet
during class</b></Default>

00:31:50.710 --> 00:31:52.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I was already in the area.</b></Default>

00:31:52.630 --> 00:31:55.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>High school's bathroom is
outside the main building?</b></Default>

00:31:55.420 --> 00:31:56.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

00:31:56.710 --> 00:31:59.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Winds are strongest
near the seashore.</b></Default>

00:32:01.670 --> 00:32:02.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

00:32:02.710 --> 00:32:04.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know you tried hard today.</b></Default>

00:32:04.630 --> 00:32:07.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I only came here to
submit my application.</b></Default>

00:32:08.039 --> 00:32:10.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right. I'm gonna
start heading home.</b></Default>

00:32:10.420 --> 00:32:11.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold it, Kaede.</b></Default>

00:32:11.670 --> 00:32:12.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's up?</b></Default>

00:32:12.670 --> 00:32:14.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you take off your glove?</b></Default>

00:32:14.170 --> 00:32:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, don't.</b></Default>

00:32:18.170 --> 00:32:19.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:32:20.789 --> 00:32:22.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It looks worse than it is.</b></Default>

00:32:22.460 --> 00:32:23.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know, Kaede...</b></Default>

00:32:23.630 --> 00:32:25.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's gonna heal up just fine.</b></Default>

00:32:25.130 --> 00:32:26.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be able to take the exam</b></Default>

00:32:27.039 --> 00:32:28.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I can commute
to high school.</b></Default>

00:32:28.880 --> 00:32:31.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please don't tell me I can't.</b></Default>

00:32:32.460 --> 00:32:34.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know I can</b></Default>

00:32:35.750 --> 00:32:38.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know I can also...
I can do...</b></Default>

00:32:38.670 --> 00:32:39.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Hey, now.</b></Default>

00:32:40.380 --> 00:32:42.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What makes this school
so special anyway?</b></Default>

00:32:44.829 --> 00:32:46.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

00:32:49.880 --> 00:32:52.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I guess the reason
doesn't matter.</b></Default>

00:32:52.579 --> 00:32:55.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't put very much thought
into what school I picked.</b></Default>

00:32:55.500 --> 00:32:57.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing, brother?</b></Default>

00:32:57.750 --> 00:32:59.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nobody said you couldn't</b></Default>

00:32:59.960 --> 00:33:01.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It didn't matter.</b></Default>

00:33:01.329 --> 00:33:03.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If this is what you want to do</b></Default>

00:33:03.789 --> 00:33:04.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>every step of the way.</b></Default>

00:33:05.000 --> 00:33:06.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if no one else likes it.</b></Default>

00:33:07.039 --> 00:33:08.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really?</b></Default>

00:33:08.130 --> 00:33:09.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really really.</b></Default>

00:33:09.710 --> 00:33:11.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But in return, you gotta
tell me what's going on</b></Default>

00:33:12.079 --> 00:33:13.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the bruises you have, okay?</b></Default>

00:33:14.460 --> 00:33:15.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:33:18.039 --> 00:33:19.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

00:33:19.380 --> 00:33:20.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] For what?</b></Default>

00:33:20.630 --> 00:33:23.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It made me happy that you got
so worried about me.</b></Default>

00:33:24.130 --> 00:33:26.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just watch your step going down.</b></Default>

00:33:26.079 --> 00:33:27.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't slip up.</b></Default>

00:33:27.250 --> 00:33:30.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't say that to me
right before I take an exam.</b></Default>

00:33:40.880 --> 00:33:42.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ soft music playing]</b></Default>

00:33:45.039 --> 00:33:46.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inaudible]</b></Default>

00:34:22.880 --> 00:34:24.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:35:12.460 --> 00:35:16.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}FEBRUARY 16TH, DAY OF THE EXAM</b></Default>

00:35:33.079 --> 00:35:35.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rise and shine. Come on.</b></Default>

00:35:36.329 --> 00:35:39.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll be late.
Today's exam day.</b></Default>

00:35:39.289 --> 00:35:42.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What time is it right now?
-7:00.</b></Default>

00:35:42.289 --> 00:35:45.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, geez. If that's the case</b></Default>

00:35:45.420 --> 00:35:48.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was so nervous</b></Default>

00:35:48.380 --> 00:35:49.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do I do?</b></Default>

00:35:49.539 --> 00:35:51.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What if I get sleepy
during the test?</b></Default>

00:35:51.539 --> 00:35:53.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure there are a bunch of
other students</b></Default>

00:35:53.630 --> 00:35:55.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who had anxiety all night, too.</b></Default>

00:35:55.380 --> 00:35:56.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't worry.</b></Default>

00:35:56.380 --> 00:35:57.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think so?</b></Default>

00:35:57.500 --> 00:35:59.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>People aren't that different.</b></Default>

00:35:59.500 --> 00:36:00.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay.</b></Default>

00:36:00.630 --> 00:36:02.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everyone feels like this?</b></Default>

00:36:03.039 --> 00:36:04.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you feel scared too?</b></Default>

00:36:05.079 --> 00:36:06.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was so nervous</b></Default>

00:36:06.329 --> 00:36:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had to go to the bathroom
mid exam.</b></Default>

00:36:08.329 --> 00:36:10.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think that would make me
more nervous.</b></Default>

00:36:10.500 --> 00:36:11.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I'm talking about poop.</b></Default>

00:36:12.000 --> 00:36:13.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Oh, you're so gross.</b></Default>

00:36:15.250 --> 00:36:16.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh! Scrambled eggs!</b></Default>

00:36:16.920 --> 00:36:18.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BOTH] Thank you for the food.</b></Default>

00:36:20.329 --> 00:36:21.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exclaims]</b></Default>

00:36:21.880 --> 00:36:24.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It tastes just like how mom
makes them.</b></Default>

00:36:24.250 --> 00:36:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's because
I asked Mai</b></Default>

00:36:25.630 --> 00:36:27.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to teach me
how to make them for you.</b></Default>

00:36:27.329 --> 00:36:28.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is so good.</b></Default>

00:36:28.539 --> 00:36:31.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right, eat quicker
or you really will be late.</b></Default>

00:36:31.250 --> 00:36:33.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It wouldn't be right
to eat these fast.</b></Default>

00:36:33.710 --> 00:36:36.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you like it that much</b></Default>

00:36:37.079 --> 00:36:38.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, if I'm being honest</b></Default>

00:36:38.880 --> 00:36:41.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>now that I've eaten a few more
bites of your scrambled eggs</b></Default>

00:36:41.630 --> 00:36:42.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai's are better.</b></Default>

00:36:42.829 --> 00:36:44.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course they are.</b></Default>

00:36:44.210 --> 00:36:46.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She is the best after all.</b></Default>

00:36:47.329 --> 00:36:49.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Here. Don't forget
to take this with you.</b></Default>

00:36:49.880 --> 00:36:51.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] What is this?</b></Default>

00:36:51.079 --> 00:36:52.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's it look like?</b></Default>

00:36:52.539 --> 00:36:53.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A lunchbox.</b></Default>

00:36:53.670 --> 00:36:54.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Correct.</b></Default>

00:36:54.630 --> 00:36:56.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After I told you yesterday
I wouldn't need one</b></Default>

00:36:57.000 --> 00:36:58.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because I'd pick up
some rice balls?</b></Default>

00:36:58.710 --> 00:37:00.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you don't want it</b></Default>

00:37:00.960 --> 00:37:02.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I do want it.</b></Default>

00:37:02.289 --> 00:37:04.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll mess up the food
if you keep shaking it.</b></Default>

00:37:06.539 --> 00:37:08.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, ah, big brother?</b></Default>

00:37:08.579 --> 00:37:09.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:37:09.670 --> 00:37:10.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks for the lunch.</b></Default>

00:37:10.880 --> 00:37:12.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's great.</b></Default>

00:37:12.210 --> 00:37:13.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm happy.</b></Default>

00:37:14.500 --> 00:37:16.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Registration number?
-Yeah.</b></Default>

00:37:16.710 --> 00:37:18.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Got your lunch?
-Got it.</b></Default>

00:37:18.710 --> 00:37:20.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your pens and pencils?</b></Default>

00:37:20.130 --> 00:37:21.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I packed them all up.</b></Default>

00:37:21.539 --> 00:37:23.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You didn't forget anything?</b></Default>

00:37:23.289 --> 00:37:24.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nope.</b></Default>

00:37:30.079 --> 00:37:31.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] That scarf is great.</b></Default>

00:37:31.960 --> 00:37:33.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] It's the one
that Mai gave me.</b></Default>

00:37:33.750 --> 00:37:35.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's nice and warm.</b></Default>

00:37:35.130 --> 00:37:37.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd expect nothing less
from Mai.</b></Default>

00:37:37.670 --> 00:37:39.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother, that's all you say.</b></Default>

00:37:40.539 --> 00:37:42.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, you did
everything you could.</b></Default>

00:37:42.710 --> 00:37:44.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So do as much as you can.</b></Default>

00:37:44.130 --> 00:37:45.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:37:45.210 --> 00:37:47.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If anything goes wrong</b></Default>

00:37:47.579 --> 00:37:48.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:37:48.829 --> 00:37:49.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See ya.</b></Default>

00:37:49.960 --> 00:37:51.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could you wait a second?</b></Default>

00:37:51.500 --> 00:37:52.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:37:53.710 --> 00:37:54.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is it?</b></Default>

00:37:55.210 --> 00:37:56.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, um, I... I just...</b></Default>

00:37:56.880 --> 00:37:57.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah?</b></Default>

00:37:58.329 --> 00:37:59.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll do this.</b></Default>

00:37:59.329 --> 00:38:00.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can do it, too.</b></Default>

00:38:00.630 --> 00:38:02.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just do it in moderation.</b></Default>

00:38:02.380 --> 00:38:04.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on. I'm trying
to be serious.</b></Default>

00:38:04.829 --> 00:38:07.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really don't want you
to hurt yourself.</b></Default>

00:38:07.420 --> 00:38:08.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:38:09.250 --> 00:38:10.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right then.</b></Default>

00:38:10.920 --> 00:38:12.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can also do my best.</b></Default>

00:38:15.460 --> 00:38:17.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, your train is here.</b></Default>

00:38:17.539 --> 00:38:20.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm-hmm. Thank you
for seeing me off.</b></Default>

00:38:34.880 --> 00:38:38.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>PREFECTURAL MINEGAHARA
HIGH SCHOOL ENTRANCE EXAM SITE</b></Default>

00:38:46.039 --> 00:38:48.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathing deeply]</b></Default>

00:38:57.539 --> 00:38:59.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[stomach grumbling]</b></Default>

00:38:59.960 --> 00:39:01.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe I'll eat something.</b></Default>

00:39:02.460 --> 00:39:03.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[meows]</b></Default>

00:39:07.000 --> 00:39:09.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ music playing on TV]</b></Default>

00:39:11.579 --> 00:39:13.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>TO THE SPECIAL VERSION OF YOU</b></Default>

00:39:14.170 --> 00:39:15.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}A special version of you...{\i0}</b></Default>

00:39:15.579 --> 00:39:18.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look at how adorable
my girl is when she's working.</b></Default>

00:39:18.670 --> 00:39:21.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[microwave dings]
-She never calls me, though.</b></Default>

00:39:21.329 --> 00:39:23.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[phone ringing]
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:39:23.960 --> 00:39:26.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could this be destiny?</b></Default>

00:39:27.210 --> 00:39:28.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>MAI SAKURAJIMA</b></Default>

00:39:28.460 --> 00:39:30.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Mai, question.</b></Default>

00:39:30.130 --> 00:39:31.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] {\i1}What?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:39:31.250 --> 00:39:33.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you know
about Valentine's Day?</b></Default>

00:39:33.500 --> 00:39:35.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is there anyone
that doesn't know?</b></Default>

00:39:35.500 --> 00:39:38.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I just wanted to make sure{\i0}
{\i1}that you did. That's all.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:39:38.130 --> 00:39:39.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know about it.</b></Default>

00:39:39.630 --> 00:39:41.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}So when is it?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:39:41.500 --> 00:39:44.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was two days ago</b></Default>

00:39:44.210 --> 00:39:45.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}And what kind of day is it?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:39:45.750 --> 00:39:47.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let me guess what
you were expecting.</b></Default>

00:39:47.630 --> 00:39:50.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I bet you wanted me to give you
