<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:48:06.750 --> 00:48:08.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] {\i1}Toyohama?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:48:08.460 --> 00:48:10.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey! It's me.</b></Default>

00:48:10.420 --> 00:48:12.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Why are you calling me?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:48:12.170 --> 00:48:14.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I need a favor.
-{\i1}Huh?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:48:14.500 --> 00:48:15.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know who to ask.</b></Default>

00:48:16.079 --> 00:48:17.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're the only one
I thought of.</b></Default>

00:48:18.789 --> 00:48:21.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>FRIDAY, FEBRUARY 20TH</b></Default>

00:48:22.130 --> 00:48:23.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

00:48:29.380 --> 00:48:31.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ music playing over earphones]</b></Default>

00:48:35.250 --> 00:48:36.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Mai!</b></Default>

00:48:36.210 --> 00:48:38.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know, you smell
really good today.</b></Default>

00:48:38.130 --> 00:48:39.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please don't smell me in public.</b></Default>

00:48:39.750 --> 00:48:41.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you listening to
on your phone?</b></Default>

00:48:41.539 --> 00:48:43.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something I heard about
at my agency.</b></Default>

00:48:43.960 --> 00:48:46.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Apparently, it's popular with
middle and high school students.</b></Default>

00:48:47.039 --> 00:48:49.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}TOKO KIRISHIMA</b></Default>

00:48:49.960 --> 00:48:52.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ music continues]</b></Default>

00:48:52.210 --> 00:48:54.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How has Kaede been feeling
about everything?</b></Default>

00:48:54.710 --> 00:48:56.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's been spiraling out
pretty hard.</b></Default>

00:48:56.960 --> 00:48:58.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

00:48:58.539 --> 00:48:59.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She really put her all in.</b></Default>

00:49:00.039 --> 00:49:01.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The hardest part of this</b></Default>

00:49:01.420 --> 00:49:03.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is that she has to get
through it on her own.</b></Default>

00:49:04.079 --> 00:49:05.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm-hmm.</b></Default>

00:49:06.130 --> 00:49:08.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry to say this, but I have
to end our date here.</b></Default>

00:49:08.880 --> 00:49:10.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can stay for at least
five more minutes.</b></Default>

00:49:11.130 --> 00:49:12.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I gotta head home.</b></Default>

00:49:12.880 --> 00:49:13.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

00:49:13.920 --> 00:49:15.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you have anything to say
before your girlfriend</b></Default>

00:49:16.000 --> 00:49:17.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>takes her entrance exams?</b></Default>

00:49:18.329 --> 00:49:19.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm rooting for you.</b></Default>

00:49:20.960 --> 00:49:22.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

00:49:23.630 --> 00:49:24.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I'm home.</b></Default>

00:49:25.670 --> 00:49:27.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cat meows, purrs]</b></Default>

00:49:31.750 --> 00:49:33.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SCHOOL BROCHURE</b></Default>

00:49:34.710 --> 00:49:35.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

00:49:35.789 --> 00:49:37.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE]
Uh, welcome home, big brother.</b></Default>

00:49:38.039 --> 00:49:40.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, good to see you.</b></Default>

00:49:43.039 --> 00:49:45.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Um, so you know...</b></Default>

00:49:45.630 --> 00:49:46.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:49:46.710 --> 00:49:48.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>About the other day...</b></Default>

00:49:48.130 --> 00:49:49.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The other day?</b></Default>

00:49:49.710 --> 00:49:51.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I went in for the exam?...</b></Default>

00:49:51.670 --> 00:49:52.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah?</b></Default>

00:49:53.289 --> 00:49:56.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to talk to you
about something I said, but...</b></Default>

00:49:59.289 --> 00:50:01.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Never mind.
Don't worry about it.</b></Default>

00:50:03.289 --> 00:50:04.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Kaede.</b></Default>

00:50:05.210 --> 00:50:06.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is it?</b></Default>

00:50:06.500 --> 00:50:08.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you free tomorrow?</b></Default>

00:50:13.000 --> 00:50:15.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SATURDAY, FEBRUARY 21ST</b></Default>

00:50:17.329 --> 00:50:19.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother</b></Default>

00:50:19.500 --> 00:50:20.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're here already.</b></Default>

00:50:21.170 --> 00:50:22.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] This is the place?</b></Default>

00:50:23.460 --> 00:50:24.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I think</b></Default>

00:50:24.539 --> 00:50:26.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it was somewhere
around here anyway.</b></Default>

00:50:27.079 --> 00:50:30.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede, come here and help me
find the event stage.</b></Default>

00:50:30.500 --> 00:50:32.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? What event?</b></Default>

00:50:32.250 --> 00:50:34.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ music playing over speakers]</b></Default>

00:50:37.250 --> 00:50:38.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's this way.</b></Default>

00:50:39.380 --> 00:50:42.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:51:12.039 --> 00:51:13.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all cheering]</b></Default>

00:51:13.789 --> 00:51:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello, everyone!</b></Default>

00:51:15.460 --> 00:51:17.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We are Sweet Bullet!</b></Default>

00:51:18.710 --> 00:51:21.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I haven't seen Nodoka
on stage before.</b></Default>

00:51:21.420 --> 00:51:22.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is great.</b></Default>

00:51:22.380 --> 00:51:24.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, the other members as well.</b></Default>

00:51:24.210 --> 00:51:26.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't believe
we're back here again.</b></Default>

00:51:26.170 --> 00:51:27.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All of us are so excited.</b></Default>

00:51:27.880 --> 00:51:29.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:51:29.329 --> 00:51:31.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? Is it just me then?</b></Default>

00:51:31.420 --> 00:51:33.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Suki, I'm confused.</b></Default>

00:51:33.460 --> 00:51:35.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you mean</b></Default>

00:51:35.170 --> 00:51:38.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What? This is where
we had our first concert.</b></Default>

00:51:39.420 --> 00:51:42.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hang on. Did that concert
not happen here? Am I wrong?</b></Default>

00:51:42.960 --> 00:51:44.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We haven't performed
here before.</b></Default>

00:51:45.000 --> 00:51:47.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No way. I bet aliens
got in my head</b></Default>

00:51:47.420 --> 00:51:48.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and messed with
my memories.</b></Default>

00:51:48.880 --> 00:51:49.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do I do?</b></Default>

00:51:49.920 --> 00:51:51.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's aliens every time with you.</b></Default>

00:51:52.000 --> 00:51:52.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd laughs]</b></Default>

00:51:53.000 --> 00:51:54.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That girl in the middle...</b></Default>

00:51:54.630 --> 00:51:57.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Regular full-time classes
didn't work for her</b></Default>

00:51:57.539 --> 00:52:00.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so she started going
to an online school.</b></Default>

00:52:00.920 --> 00:52:02.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I went to this
one orientation</b></Default>

00:52:02.670 --> 00:52:03.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>without telling you</b></Default>

00:52:04.170 --> 00:52:06.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I happened to see her in
a student interview.</b></Default>

00:52:07.079 --> 00:52:08.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, wow, really?</b></Default>

00:52:08.829 --> 00:52:11.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, well, let's move on
to our next song.</b></Default>

00:52:11.579 --> 00:52:13.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is the last one of the day</b></Default>

00:52:13.670 --> 00:52:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so let's burn it out.</b></Default>

00:52:15.380 --> 00:52:16.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

00:52:16.829 --> 00:52:18.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ music playing]</b></Default>

00:52:19.920 --> 00:52:21.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Listen</b></Default>

00:52:21.210 --> 00:52:22.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Minegahara high school</b></Default>

00:52:23.380 --> 00:52:25.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if that's the school you feel
you want to go to</b></Default>

00:52:25.880 --> 00:52:28.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll cheer you on
with everything I've got.</b></Default>

00:52:28.329 --> 00:52:31.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Well, isn't the exam
already over?</b></Default>

00:52:31.210 --> 00:52:33.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I'm sure there'll be
a second round of registration.</b></Default>

00:52:33.789 --> 00:52:34.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Kaede sighs]</b></Default>

00:52:34.880 --> 00:52:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] But if attending
Minegahara High isn't something</b></Default>

00:52:37.880 --> 00:52:39.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that this version of yourself
wants to do</b></Default>

00:52:40.039 --> 00:52:42.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you don't have to force yourself
into going.</b></Default>

00:52:42.789 --> 00:52:45.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai and Toyohama
feel the same way.</b></Default>

00:52:45.329 --> 00:52:47.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Think about Dad and Tomobe.</b></Default>

00:52:47.289 --> 00:52:49.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They don't want something
like that.</b></Default>

00:52:49.380 --> 00:52:52.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And really, I don't think
the other Kaede does either.</b></Default>

00:52:53.039 --> 00:52:53.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:52:54.380 --> 00:52:55.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As long as the person
you are now</b></Default>

00:52:56.000 --> 00:52:58.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is still able to keep
finding joy in little things</b></Default>

00:52:58.789 --> 00:53:01.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm fine with whatever
you choose.</b></Default>

00:53:01.289 --> 00:53:03.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want you to go out there
and have fun.</b></Default>

00:53:03.500 --> 00:53:05.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want you to laugh
at the silliest things</b></Default>

00:53:05.630 --> 00:53:06.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and enjoy your life.</b></Default>

00:53:07.000 --> 00:53:08.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's all I care about.</b></Default>

00:53:09.710 --> 00:53:12.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's just imagine
you did get accepted.</b></Default>

00:53:12.289 --> 00:53:14.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If going to a school
like that only makes things</b></Default>

00:53:14.130 --> 00:53:15.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>harder for you</b></Default>

00:53:15.079 --> 00:53:17.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't be happy about that.</b></Default>

00:53:17.250 --> 00:53:19.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess. But then I...</b></Default>

00:53:19.670 --> 00:53:21.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I do want to have
that experience</b></Default>

00:53:21.500 --> 00:53:22.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>everyone else gets.</b></Default>

00:53:23.170 --> 00:53:25.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's embarrassing for me
to be different.</b></Default>

00:53:25.630 --> 00:53:27.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you saying
that girl up there</b></Default>

00:53:27.210 --> 00:53:28.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>should be embarrassed?</b></Default>

00:53:32.920 --> 00:53:35.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, because I think
she is amazing.</b></Default>

00:53:35.170 --> 00:53:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even though she's different
from everyone else?</b></Default>

00:53:38.289 --> 00:53:39.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know.</b></Default>

00:53:39.789 --> 00:53:42.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, why don't you wait until
after you talk to her</b></Default>

00:53:42.670 --> 00:53:44.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to make big decisions?</b></Default>

00:53:44.210 --> 00:53:45.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Talk to her?</b></Default>

00:53:45.380 --> 00:53:46.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I asked Toyohama.</b></Default>

00:53:47.039 --> 00:53:49.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said Uzuki would
give us some time.</b></Default>

00:53:49.130 --> 00:53:50.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to get to
know the school.</b></Default>

00:53:50.880 --> 00:53:52.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We could ask her
some questions.</b></Default>

00:53:54.920 --> 00:53:56.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ music continues]</b></Default>

00:54:02.670 --> 00:54:04.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[music ends]
-[all cheering]</b></Default>

00:54:05.960 --> 00:54:07.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[KAEDE]Big brother?
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:54:07.829 --> 00:54:09.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] You really
won't be upset</b></Default>

00:54:09.210 --> 00:54:10.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if I don't go to Minegahara?</b></Default>

00:54:11.829 --> 00:54:14.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Every day the other
Kaede was around</b></Default>

00:54:14.289 --> 00:54:15.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she put in 100%.</b></Default>

00:54:16.789 --> 00:54:19.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She woke up in a hospital bed
out of nowhere.</b></Default>

00:54:19.460 --> 00:54:21.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She didn't know who or
where she was.</b></Default>

00:54:21.329 --> 00:54:23.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I bet she was probably
pretty scared.</b></Default>

00:54:23.880 --> 00:54:26.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All of that is a lot to take in.</b></Default>

00:54:26.210 --> 00:54:28.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Mm-hmm.
-Oh, man.</b></Default>

00:54:28.079 --> 00:54:29.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She did everything
she possibly could</b></Default>

00:54:30.079 --> 00:54:31.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to be my little sister.</b></Default>

00:54:31.920 --> 00:54:33.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And by filling that role</b></Default>

00:54:33.789 --> 00:54:36.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede turned me
into a big brother.</b></Default>

00:54:36.750 --> 00:54:38.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE]
My other self sounds...</b></Default>

00:54:38.630 --> 00:54:39.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>really amazing.</b></Default>

00:54:40.039 --> 00:54:42.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] So when
that Kaede disappeared</b></Default>

00:54:42.079 --> 00:54:44.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't help but be sad.</b></Default>

00:54:44.460 --> 00:54:46.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I cried so many tears.</b></Default>

00:54:46.579 --> 00:54:49.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel like I'm gonna choke up
talking about it.</b></Default>

00:54:50.250 --> 00:54:52.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess you do like her more.</b></Default>

00:54:52.130 --> 00:54:53.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you know, Kaede</b></Default>

00:54:53.380 --> 00:54:55.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as much as I had cried over it</b></Default>

00:54:55.750 --> 00:54:57.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I felt just as much relief.</b></Default>

00:54:57.920 --> 00:55:00.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I was really happy.
-Huh?</b></Default>

00:55:00.579 --> 00:55:03.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because the Kaede I knew
was finally back.</b></Default>

00:55:04.380 --> 00:55:06.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that true? Really?</b></Default>

00:55:06.789 --> 00:55:08.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course it is.</b></Default>

00:55:08.460 --> 00:55:09.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on.</b></Default>

00:55:09.630 --> 00:55:11.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What kind of guy
do you think I am?</b></Default>

00:55:11.880 --> 00:55:13.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How was I supposed to know?</b></Default>

00:55:13.829 --> 00:55:17.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't know. Not if you never
tell me anything.</b></Default>

00:55:17.630 --> 00:55:20.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This whole time, I thought
you liked my other self</b></Default>

00:55:20.289 --> 00:55:21.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>better than you liked me.</b></Default>

00:55:22.039 --> 00:55:24.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And... I thought that...</b></Default>

00:55:24.539 --> 00:55:27.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought I had to try
and be her replacement.</b></Default>

00:55:27.500 --> 00:55:29.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stop overthinking this.</b></Default>

00:55:29.170 --> 00:55:31.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't like one more
than the other.</b></Default>

00:55:31.250 --> 00:55:33.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Really?
-You're both regular girls.</b></Default>

00:55:33.789 --> 00:55:35.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What does that mean?</b></Default>

00:55:35.210 --> 00:55:37.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Both of you are
my little sisters</b></Default>

00:55:37.210 --> 00:55:38.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I like you both the same.</b></Default>

00:55:39.079 --> 00:55:41.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides, talking about
my sister all the time</b></Default>

00:55:41.460 --> 00:55:42.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is sounding kind of weird.</b></Default>

00:55:44.960 --> 00:55:46.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

00:55:48.500 --> 00:55:50.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, you know what, big brother?</b></Default>

00:55:50.750 --> 00:55:52.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hmm?
-I thought of something.</b></Default>

00:55:52.670 --> 00:55:54.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to go
to the zoo sometime.</b></Default>

