by the people around you.</b></Default>

01:02:17.579 --> 01:02:19.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Only you can make you happy."</b></Default>

01:02:19.460 --> 01:02:21.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]
Now that's a heck of a mom.</b></Default>

01:02:21.670 --> 01:02:23.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NODOKA]
Yeah, man, she's super cool.</b></Default>

01:02:23.710 --> 01:02:25.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Okay, so the reason</b></Default>

01:02:25.329 --> 01:02:26.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you chose to go to
your current school</b></Default>

01:02:27.039 --> 01:02:28.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was because your mom showed you.</b></Default>

01:02:28.829 --> 01:02:30.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was thanks to Nodoka, too.</b></Default>

01:02:30.670 --> 01:02:32.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh?
-And not just her, either.</b></Default>

01:02:32.789 --> 01:02:35.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All of the Sweet Bullet members
were really supportive.</b></Default>

01:02:35.960 --> 01:02:37.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I wasn't able
to go to school</b></Default>

01:02:38.000 --> 01:02:40.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all of them were there
to stick it out with me</b></Default>

01:02:40.630 --> 01:02:42.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the fans are
a part of it too.</b></Default>

01:02:43.170 --> 01:02:45.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had a hard time fitting in
in my old school</b></Default>

01:02:45.420 --> 01:02:46.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but after a while</b></Default>

01:02:47.039 --> 01:02:50.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I had my group members</b></Default>

01:02:51.039 --> 01:02:54.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're everyone that I know</b></Default>

01:02:54.420 --> 01:02:56.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There might be even
more "everyones"</b></Default>

01:02:56.250 --> 01:02:57.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I haven't gotten
to meet yet.</b></Default>

01:02:57.960 --> 01:02:59.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I had that thought</b></Default>

01:02:59.460 --> 01:03:01.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's when I decided to go
to this school.</b></Default>

01:03:02.039 --> 01:03:04.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that's about it.</b></Default>

01:03:05.170 --> 01:03:07.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would it be okay if I asked you
one more thing?</b></Default>

01:03:07.960 --> 01:03:09.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ask as much as you want.</b></Default>

01:03:09.579 --> 01:03:11.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to know, um</b></Default>

01:03:11.750 --> 01:03:14.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>between the you that
went to the old school</b></Default>

01:03:14.380 --> 01:03:16.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the you that goes
to the new school</b></Default>

01:03:16.500 --> 01:03:18.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>which do you like better?</b></Default>

01:03:18.079 --> 01:03:20.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could never choose
one over the other.</b></Default>

01:03:20.670 --> 01:03:22.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My past self worked hard
to get here.</b></Default>

01:03:23.000 --> 01:03:24.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now my current self exists.</b></Default>

01:03:24.920 --> 01:03:26.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

01:03:29.420 --> 01:03:30.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I get it.</b></Default>

01:03:30.880 --> 01:03:32.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are so right.</b></Default>

01:03:32.460 --> 01:03:35.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm-hmm. It's the truth.
[chuckles]</b></Default>

01:03:45.500 --> 01:03:49.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SATURDAY, FEBRUARY 28TH</b></Default>

01:03:52.829 --> 01:03:54.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Look, there's Komi!</b></Default>

01:03:54.960 --> 01:03:56.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Komi!</b></Default>

01:03:56.250 --> 01:03:58.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede! It's been two months.</b></Default>

01:03:58.380 --> 01:04:00.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yep. Thank you so much
for coming.</b></Default>

01:04:00.750 --> 01:04:02.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course I'd come here.</b></Default>

01:04:02.329 --> 01:04:04.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was so happy
to get that email.</b></Default>

01:04:04.960 --> 01:04:06.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And thank you so much</b></Default>

01:04:06.250 --> 01:04:08.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for coming here with her
to pick me up.</b></Default>

01:04:08.710 --> 01:04:09.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No worries.</b></Default>

01:04:09.829 --> 01:04:12.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had to make a run to buy stuff
at the supermarket anyway.</b></Default>

01:04:14.039 --> 01:04:14.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

01:04:15.039 --> 01:04:16.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello! Welcome, Kotomi.</b></Default>

01:04:16.880 --> 01:04:18.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks for the invite.</b></Default>

01:04:19.289 --> 01:04:21.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, did you buy
soy sauce?</b></Default>

01:04:21.250 --> 01:04:22.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did.</b></Default>

01:04:22.500 --> 01:04:24.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you send your emails
with this?</b></Default>

01:04:24.380 --> 01:04:25.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, Mai gave it to me.</b></Default>

01:04:26.170 --> 01:04:28.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not brand-new or anything</b></Default>

01:04:28.130 --> 01:04:30.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I don't use it</b></Default>

01:04:31.130 --> 01:04:32.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Check this out, Komi.</b></Default>

01:04:32.630 --> 01:04:34.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a page about the school.</b></Default>

01:04:34.170 --> 01:04:35.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KOTOMI] That's amazing.</b></Default>

01:04:35.630 --> 01:04:37.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can take classes
on all this stuff?</b></Default>

01:04:38.079 --> 01:04:39.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you can do it online.</b></Default>

01:04:39.710 --> 01:04:41.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look, I even have
a homeroom teacher.</b></Default>

01:04:42.210 --> 01:04:44.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can take the courses
I want at my own pace.</b></Default>

01:04:44.670 --> 01:04:46.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And for fields
I'm interested in</b></Default>

01:04:46.130 --> 01:04:47.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I get lessons
from vocational schools</b></Default>

01:04:48.079 --> 01:04:49.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that have ties to this one.</b></Default>

01:04:49.539 --> 01:04:50.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really incredible.</b></Default>

01:04:51.039 --> 01:04:52.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know, right?</b></Default>

01:04:52.250 --> 01:04:54.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look at this, I can do all sorts
of studying.</b></Default>

01:04:54.880 --> 01:04:56.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. You're incredible.</b></Default>

01:04:56.880 --> 01:04:57.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am?</b></Default>

01:04:58.000 --> 01:04:59.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, I didn't do
this much research</b></Default>

01:04:59.920 --> 01:05:01.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when I picked out
my high school.</b></Default>

01:05:01.710 --> 01:05:03.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My teacher saw my grades
and told me</b></Default>

01:05:03.789 --> 01:05:05.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>which one I should go to</b></Default>

01:05:05.289 --> 01:05:06.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I just went with that.</b></Default>

01:05:07.000 --> 01:05:09.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede, you're so independent.</b></Default>

01:05:10.000 --> 01:05:11.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

01:05:12.789 --> 01:05:14.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone ringing]</b></Default>

01:05:15.829 --> 01:05:17.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone continues ringing]</b></Default>

01:05:21.079 --> 01:05:22.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Miss Miwako.</b></Default>

01:05:22.710 --> 01:05:24.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you mind
if I answer the phone?</b></Default>

01:05:24.670 --> 01:05:26.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Please do.</b></Default>

01:05:29.579 --> 01:05:30.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, hello?</b></Default>

01:05:30.880 --> 01:05:32.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawas.</b></Default>

01:05:33.289 --> 01:05:34.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, hello.</b></Default>

01:05:34.579 --> 01:05:35.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is Kaede.</b></Default>

01:05:35.829 --> 01:05:37.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, my big brother
is here.</b></Default>

01:05:37.880 --> 01:05:40.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought I should answer
since I saw your name.</b></Default>

01:05:40.880 --> 01:05:41.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

01:05:42.670 --> 01:05:44.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh, I got accepted?</b></Default>

01:05:44.829 --> 01:05:45.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BOTH] Huh?</b></Default>

01:05:46.039 --> 01:05:47.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

01:05:48.420 --> 01:05:49.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay.</b></Default>

01:05:50.250 --> 01:05:52.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She wants to speak to you.</b></Default>

01:05:54.130 --> 01:05:55.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta here.</b></Default>

01:05:55.630 --> 01:05:57.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIWAKO] {\i1}I wanted to say{\i0}
{\i1}congratulations.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:05:57.960 --> 01:06:00.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Kaede got accepted to{\i0}
{\i1}Minegahara High School.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:06:00.920 --> 01:06:02.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? She did?</b></Default>

01:06:02.710 --> 01:06:05.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}It turns out they fell short{\i0}
{\i1}on their quota.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:06:05.210 --> 01:06:06.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you said
it was going to be</b></Default>

01:06:07.039 --> 01:06:08.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>really competitive this year.</b></Default>

01:06:08.500 --> 01:06:10.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}The number{\i0}
{\i1}of initial applicants{\i0}</b></Default>

01:06:10.210 --> 01:06:11.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}was over double their limit</b></Default>

01:06:11.920 --> 01:06:14.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}so lots of students{\i0}
{\i1}avoided applying altogether.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:06:14.710 --> 01:06:17.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}There were social media{\i0}
{\i1}campaigns from hopefuls{\i0}</b></Default>

01:06:17.210 --> 01:06:19.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}telling other kids{\i0}
{\i1}they wouldn't make it in{\i0}</b></Default>

01:06:19.289 --> 01:06:20.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}if they applied.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:06:20.460 --> 01:06:21.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did they, now?</b></Default>

01:06:21.750 --> 01:06:23.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Regardless of how it{\i0}
{\i1}all happened</b></Default>

01:06:23.710 --> 01:06:26.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Kaede still got accepted{\i0}
{\i1}to Minegahara High.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:06:26.250 --> 01:06:27.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

01:06:27.380 --> 01:06:28.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}There is paperwork to fill out</b></Default>

01:06:29.039 --> 01:06:31.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}so when she decides what to do</b></Default>

01:06:31.500 --> 01:06:34.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course. Let me
talk it out with Kaede.</b></Default>

01:06:42.880 --> 01:06:44.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother, I...</b></Default>

01:06:45.210 --> 01:06:47.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't want to go
to Minegahara.</b></Default>

01:06:47.789 --> 01:06:50.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to go to the school
I'll find myself.</b></Default>

01:06:51.420 --> 01:06:53.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ piano music playing]</b></Default>

01:06:55.579 --> 01:06:56.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then, Kaede...</b></Default>

01:06:56.750 --> 01:06:58.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAN] {\i1}The school didn't meet{\i0}
{\i1}their quota?{\i0}</b></Default>

01:06:58.460 --> 01:06:59.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Yeah.</b></Default>

01:06:59.630 --> 01:07:01.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tomobe said she wanted
an answer sooner than later</b></Default>

01:07:02.039 --> 01:07:04.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because of the paperwork
and stuff.</b></Default>

01:07:04.329 --> 01:07:07.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>About that, I was thinking
of giving you a call tonight.</b></Default>

01:07:07.960 --> 01:07:09.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you come over tomorrow?</b></Default>

01:07:09.750 --> 01:07:13.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure thing. I'll see
your mother at the hospital.</b></Default>

01:07:13.539 --> 01:07:14.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I'll head over.</b></Default>

01:07:14.710 --> 01:07:15.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then after that...</b></Default>

01:07:16.039 --> 01:07:18.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right, girls, it's time
for me to get to Benny's.</b></Default>

01:07:18.789 --> 01:07:21.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, then I'll go ahead
and leave now, too.</b></Default>

01:07:21.130 --> 01:07:24.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My mother told me I shouldn't
do anything to trouble you guys</b></Default>

01:07:24.130 --> 01:07:25.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>while I'm here.</b></Default>

01:07:25.079 --> 01:07:27.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You couldn't do anything
to trouble us.</b></Default>

01:07:31.130 --> 01:07:32.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede is so amazing.</b></Default>

01:07:33.000 --> 01:07:33.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She is?</b></Default>

01:07:34.000 --> 01:07:36.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm trying to imagine myself
in her shoes.</b></Default>

01:07:36.460 --> 01:07:38.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I would've said
that I still wanted to try</b></Default>

01:07:38.710 --> 01:07:40.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>going to a full-time school.</b></Default>

01:07:40.380 --> 01:07:41.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that 'cause
you feel comfortable</b></Default>

01:07:41.880 --> 01:07:43.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you don't stand out?</b></Default>

01:07:43.289 --> 01:07:44.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

01:07:44.250 --> 01:07:47.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, there are a lot of things
that lined up for Kaede.</b></Default>

01:07:48.000 --> 01:07:49.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She got the chance
to hear stories</b></Default>

01:07:49.920 --> 01:07:52.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about an online high school
from someone.</b></Default>

01:07:52.329 --> 01:07:55.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But still, I guess the fact
she chose her path</b></Default>

01:07:55.539 --> 01:07:57.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>makes her pretty amazing.</b></Default>

01:07:57.130 --> 01:07:59.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, you should definitely
tell Kaede that.</b></Default>

01:07:59.750 --> 01:08:01.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure it'd make her happy.</b></Default>

01:08:01.539 --> 01:08:03.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No way. She'll take it too far.</b></Default>

01:08:03.750 --> 01:08:05.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I'll just have to
tell her myself.</b></Default>

01:08:07.789 --> 01:08:09.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Uh. Hold on.
-Oh.</b></Default>

01:08:09.420 --> 01:08:10.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She already replied to me.</b></Default>

01:08:11.039 --> 01:08:12.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What did she say?</b></Default>

01:08:12.170 --> 01:08:14.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's asking if it was
her real big brother</b></Default>

01:08:14.250 --> 01:08:16.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who said that.
Sounds like a fake.</b></Default>

01:08:17.000 --> 01:08:19.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm. Well, I guess that means
Kaede has the ability</b></Default>

01:08:20.079 --> 01:08:21.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to tell a joke now.</b></Default>

01:08:26.789 --> 01:08:29.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We made an effort to be
in line early, too.</b></Default>

01:08:29.670 --> 01:08:31.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing to be done
if they're all sold out.</b></Default>

01:08:32.039 --> 01:08:34.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

01:08:34.250 --> 01:08:36.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come with me
when I get revenge, Kaede.</b></Default>

01:08:36.380 --> 01:08:37.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Okay.</b></Default>

01:08:37.329 --> 01:08:39.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't wait for the
limited edition parfait.</b></Default>

01:08:39.789 --> 01:08:42.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>KAEDE AZUSAGAWA</b></Default>

01:08:47.380 --> 01:08:50.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}[♪ closing theme song playing]</b></Default>

01:12:47.539 --> 01:12:50.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>MARCH 1ST</b></Default>

01:12:50.710 --> 01:12:52.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]
So this is the last time</b></Default>

01:12:52.460 --> 01:12:54.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll see you in
school uniform.</b></Default>

01:12:54.130 --> 01:12:55.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And today is the last day</b></Default>

01:12:55.789 --> 01:12:57.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I get to go home
from school with you.</b></Default>

01:12:57.710 --> 01:12:59.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shall we have one final walk
together?</b></Default>

01:12:59.960 --> 01:13:02.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait for me at the beach
after the ceremony.</b></Default>

01:13:14.289 --> 01:13:15.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

01:13:25.500 --> 01:13:26.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai, is that you?</b></Default>

01:13:29.960 --> 01:13:31.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hi, mister.</b></Default>

01:13:31.130 --> 01:13:32.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do I know you?</b></Default>

01:13:43.289 --> 01:13:46.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NEXT MOVIE RASCAL DOES NOT
DREAM OF A KNAPSACK KID</b></Default>
